Description: Activation of Modulo function.0 / Modulo Off /oFF: Modulo is off1 / Modulo On /on: Modulo is onSetting can only be modified if power stage isdisabled.Modified settings become active immediately.Available with firmware version ≥V01.01.
Parameter address via fieldbus: CANopen 3006:38hModbus 1648Profibus 1648CIP 106.1.56ModbusTCP 1648EtherCAT 3006:38hPROFINET 1648
